OL,5, The chancellor has threatened to hit   
OL,6, energy companies with a one-off        
OL,7, "windfall" tax if they don't invest    
OL,8, enough in new projects.                
OL,10,FRishi Sunak added that he wanted to see
OL,11,Finvestment "soon" to boost energy      
OL,12,Fsecurity, and "no options are off the  
OL,13,Ftable" if not.                         
OL,15,FOpposition parties want to tax oil and 
OL,16,Fgas firms' soaring profits to help     
OL,17,Fhouseholds grappling with rising bills.
OL,19,FTreasury officials have been ordered to
OL,20,Fexamine a potential tax, a source said.
